 experience at deutsche bank they oversaw a multibillion dollar portfolio and were instrumental in the firms participation in complex restructurings and reorganizations such as lehman brothers enron visteon and refco mr martin joined deutsche bank as a distressed investment analyst in  rising to the position of distressed trader and portfolio manager before being named cohead of the distressed products group in    mr martin holds a bs in commerce from the university of virginia and an mba from columbia business school mr lanktree began his career at salomon smith barney as an investment banking analyst in its telecom and media group in   he joined deutsche bank in  as a distressed investment analyst  after serving as a distressed trader and portfolio manager he was named cohead along with mr martin in   mr lanktree holds a bba in finance and a ba in computer applications from the university of notre dame about solus alternative asset management lp solus alternative asset management lp solus is a new yorkbased secregistered independent investment management firm specializing in event and creditrelated investment strategies with  professionals as of march   solus manages  billion in assets for a diversified group of institutional investors and family offices worldwide solus was founded in june of  when the hedge fund strategies group of stanfield capital partners llc separated to form an independent firm under the continued leadership of christopher pucillo source solus alternative asset management lp view table fullscreen view table fullscreen journalists and bloggers the news you need when you need it join pr newswire for journalists to access all of the free services designated to make your job easier in need of subject matter experts for your story submit a free profnet request and find the sources you need learn more my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distributi